2009-07-04  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	Fix loading of the versioned python module.

	* configure.ac:
	* glom/Makefile.am:
	* glom/python_embed/Makefile.am:
	* glom/python_embed/glom_python.cc:
	* glom/python_embed/python_module/Makefile.am:
