	* glom/utility_widgets/db_adddel/db_adddel.cc:
	* glom/utility_widgets/db_adddel/glom_db_treemodel.cc:
	Use Gtk::TreeModel::iterator instead of Gtk::TreeIter 
	and Gtk::TreeModel::Path instead of Gtk::TreePath, for 
	consistency.

